{"tid":1250410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"謎底解開！救護員等約20分鐘　郭家麒引述警方指需找鎖匙","createTime":"2019-06-22T05:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T10:53:58.000Z","uid":5195,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b4d9203f655bb402eeb2d49adfb19bec4987a28c","tid":1250410,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:22:52.000Z","msg":"公民黨立法會議員郭家麒表示，警方晚上召救護車時，一度打算安排救護車於警察總部西閘出入，但西閘有大量路障，於是救護人員按示威者建議，轉往正門。<br />\n<br />\n救護人員於正門等候約20分鐘才能進入警察總部，郭家麒引述警方解釋指，需時尋回警察總部大閘的鎖匙。<br />\n<br />\n郭家麒又指，開閘時警方一度計劃派出防暴警察於閘外戒備，但他與工黨張超雄勸止，以免激化示威者情緒。"},{"pid":"6468b4c053c664f197b2f9a8b6457466066ae349","tid":1250410,"uid":2267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:37:19.000Z","msg":"啲狗嘅正面形象，喺呢個運動起徹底改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43563cde9ea8871378f09029f285fa611456b301","tid":1250410,"uid":20696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:38:10.000Z","msg":"諗住唔會讓開所以鎖匙都無諗住搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12038c9472bff59a4b8a2175d6a56eb7db46695","tid":1250410,"uid":128388,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:05:33.000Z","msg":"自己鎖自己跟住無鎖鑰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1fd6e5910f6175482cdebc3535b8ecbf6e755b3","tid":1250410,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲狗真係on9"},{"pid":"00d771ec3a12b8267e0c658a7025729932cd0a4d","tid":1250410,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep